<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Haven" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Haven,</orth> harbour, port, place of safety: <bibl n="shak. shr 5.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 1, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.276" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 276</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.7.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 7, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 3</bibl> (only in Q<hi rend="sub">1</hi>; the other O. Edd. <emph>heaven</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ant 4.10.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 10, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.171" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 49</bibl>. cf. <emph>Milford Haven.</emph>
